<br>
My feeling is that I would probably never use DC to solo (unless I was farming something and the best pet I could find was also dire charmable) but that it might be a good option in groups where you need to do crowd control, and slows, and as a result you might not have the spare mana to deal with re-charms 100 percent of the time they are needed. <br>
<br>
If there was a multi-mob pull that wiped your xp group because you were busy trying to recharm the hasted, angry mob that used to be your pet, people would probably wonder if that charmed pet was such a great idea after all. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.showPrevMessage?topicID=52.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.showNextMessage?topicID=52.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=52.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.pwshift.com/tr/images/mt/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.emailToFriend?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.threadControl?topicID=52.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/posticons/techops.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=52.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub169.ezboard.com/fmtboardsfrm22.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=52.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub169.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="mtboardsfrm1">General<option value="mtboardsfrm2">Market<option value="mtboardsfrm3">Rants<option value="mt